{"pageProps":{"header":{"title":"OpenLayers를 여행하는 개발자를 위한 안내서 - 21. WFS Transaction으로 데이터 수정하기","excerpt":"세 가지 WFS Transaction API 중, 데이터를 수정하는 Update에 대해 다뤄보자.","coverImage":"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/50317129/156607880-c5abad92-1991-4c01-b85f-7153bf89cb64.png","date":"2022-05-31T01:10:12+09:00","type":"projects","category":"GIS","tag":["GIS","GeoServer","OpenLayers","WFS"],"group":"OpenLayers를 여행하는 개발자를 위한 안내서","comment":true,"publish":true},"name":"2022-05-31-gis-guide-for-programmer-21.md","url":["2022-05-31-gis-guide-for-programmer-21","2022","05","31","gis-guide-for-programmer-21"],"toc":"<ul><li><a href=\"#개요\">개요</a></li><li><a href=\"#공간정보-데이터 수정하기\">공간정보 데이터 수정하기</a></li><ul><li><a href=\"#1.-WFS Transaction Update URL 구성하기\">1. WFS Transaction Update URL 구성하기</a></li><li><a href=\"#2.-Snap과 Modify 기능 추가하기\">2. Snap과 Modify 기능 추가하기</a></li><li><a href=\"#3.-Snap과 Modify 객체에 이벤트 붙이기\">3. Snap과 Modify 객체에 이벤트 붙이기</a></li></ul><li><a href=\"#예제-확인하기\">예제 확인하기</a></li></ul>","content":"<h1 id=\"개요\">개요 <a href=\"#개요\">🔗</a></h1><p>세 가지 WFS Transaction API 중, 데이터를 수정하는 Update에 대해 다뤄보자.</p>\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<h1 id=\"공간정보-데이터 수정하기\">공간정보 데이터 수정하기 <a href=\"#공간정보-데이터 수정하기\">🔗</a></h1><p>WFS Transaction 프로토콜을 활용하면, 공간정보 데이터를 DB가 아닌 웹/앱 등 API 호출이 가능한 다양한 환경에서 데이터를 수정할 수 있다.</p>\n<p>본 문서에서의 처리 방식은 아래와 같다.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>객체를 클릭하면 나타나는 <code class=\"inline-code\">Overlay</code> 안의 수정 버튼을 클릭한다.</li>\n<li>원하는 모양으로 <code class=\"inline-code\">Polygon</code>을 수정한다.<ol>\n<li>본 문서에서는 <code class=\"inline-code\">Polygon</code> 형태만을 다룬다.</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>수정할 데이터를 작성한다.</li>\n<li>WFS Transaction Update를 통해 데이터를 수정한다.</li>\n</ol>\n<br />\n<br />\n\n\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"1.-WFS Transaction Update URL 구성하기\">1. WFS Transaction Update URL 구성하기 <a href=\"#1.-WFS Transaction Update URL 구성하기\">🔗</a></h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"codeblock\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"top\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>TXT</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<button onclick=\"copyCode(this);\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 384 512\" data-icon=\"clipboard\" class=\"i-clipboard\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M336 64h-80c0-35.3-28.7-64-64-64s-64 28.7-64 64H48C21.5 64 0 85.5 0 112v352c0 26.5 21.5 48 48 48h288c26.5 0 48-21.5 48-48V112c0-26.5-21.5-48-48-48zM192 40c13.3 0 24 10.7 24 24s-10.7 24-24 24-24-10.7-24-24 10.7-24 24-24zm144 418c0 3.3-2.7 6-6 6H54c-3.3 0-6-2.7-6-6V118c0-3.3 2.7-6 6-6h42v36c0 6.6 5.4 12 12 12h168c6.6 0 12-5.4 12-12v-36h42c3.3 0 6 2.7 6 6z\"></path></svg></button>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<pre class=\"language-txt\"><table><tbody><tr data-number=0><td class=\"line-number\" data-number=\"0\">0</td><td class=\"line-code\" data-number=0>POST https://example.com/geoserver/wfs</td></tr></tbody></table></pre>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"codeblock\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"top\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>XML</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<button onclick=\"copyCode(this);\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 384 512\" data-icon=\"clipboard\" class=\"i-clipboard\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M336 64h-80c0-35.3-28.7-64-64-64s-64 28.7-64 64H48C21.5 64 0 85.5 0 112v352c0 26.5 21.5 48 48 48h288c26.5 0 48-21.5 48-48V112c0-26.5-21.5-48-48-48zM192 40c13.3 0 24 10.7 24 24s-10.7 24-24 24-24-10.7-24-24 10.7-24 24-24zm144 418c0 3.3-2.7 6-6 6H54c-3.3 0-6-2.7-6-6V118c0-3.3 2.7-6 6-6h42v36c0 6.6 5.4 12 12 12h168c6.6 0 12-5.4 12-12v-36h42c3.3 0 6 2.7 6 6z\"></path></svg></button>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<pre class=\"language-xml\"><table><tbody><tr data-number=0><td class=\"line-number\" data-number=\"0\">0</td><td class=\"line-code\" data-number=0><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token namespace\">wfs:</span>Transaction</span></td></tr>\n<tr data-number=1><td class=\"line-number\" data-number=\"1\">1</td><td class=\"line-code\" data-number=1>    <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">xmlns:</span>wfs</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.opengis.net/wfs<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></td></tr>\n<tr data-number=2><td class=\"line-number\" data-number=\"2\">2</td><td class=\"line-code\" data-number=2>    <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">xmlns:</span>gml</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.opengis.net/gml<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></td></tr>\n<tr data-number=3><td class=\"line-number\" data-number=\"3\">3</td><td class=\"line-code\" data-number=3>    <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">xmlns:</span>ogc</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.opengis.net/ogc<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></td></tr>\n<tr data-number=4><td class=\"line-number\" data-number=\"4\">4</td><td class=\"line-code\" data-number=4>    <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">xmlns:</span>xsi</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></td></tr>\n<tr data-number=5><td class=\"line-number\" data-number=\"5\">5</td><td class=\"line-code\" data-number=5>    <span class=\"token attr-name\">service</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>WFS<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></td></tr>\n<tr data-number=6><td class=\"line-number\" data-number=\"6\">6</td><td class=\"line-code\" data-number=6>    <span class=\"token attr-name\">version</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>1.0.0<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></td></tr>\n<tr data-number=7><td class=\"line-number\" data-number=\"7\">7</td><td class=\"line-code\" data-number=7>    <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">xsi:</span>schemaLocation</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.opengis.net/wfs http://schemas.opengis.net/wfs/1.0.0/WFS-transaction.xsd<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></td></tr>\n<tr data-number=8><td class=\"line-number\" data-number=\"8\">8</td><td class=\"line-code\" data-number=8>    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token namespace\">wfs:</span>Update</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">typeName</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>layer_name<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></td></tr>\n<tr data-number=9><td class=\"line-number\" data-number=\"9\">9</td><td class=\"line-code\" data-number=9>        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token namespace\">wfs:</span>Property</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></td></tr>\n<tr data-number=10><td class=\"line-number\" data-number=\"10\">10</td><td class=\"line-code\" data-number=10>            <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token namespace\">wfs:</span>Name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>column1<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token namespace\">wfs:</span>Name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></td></tr>\n<tr data-number=11><td class=\"line-number\" data-number=\"11\">11</td><td class=\"line-code\" data-number=11>            <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token namespace\">wfs:</span>Value</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>value1<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token namespace\">wfs:</span>Value</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></td></tr>\n<tr data-number=12><td class=\"line-number\" data-number=\"12\">12</td><td class=\"line-code\" data-number=12>        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token namespace\">wfs:</span>Property</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></td></tr>\n<tr data-number=13><td class=\"line-number\" data-number=\"13\">13</td><td class=\"line-code\" data-number=13></td></tr>\n<tr data-number=14><td class=\"line-number\" data-number=\"14\">14</td><td class=\"line-code\" data-number=14>        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token namespace\">wfs:</span>Property</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></td></tr>\n<tr data-number=15><td class=\"line-number\" data-number=\"15\">15</td><td class=\"line-code\" data-number=15>            <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token namespace\">wfs:</span>Name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></s